plot: This concert was filmed September 26, 1998. It was performed at Wembley Stadium infront of over 52,000 fans. I love it!! The setlist is Opening Music, If You Cant Dance, Who Do You Think YOu Are, Something Kinda Funny, Do It, Too Much, Stop, Where Did Our Love Go, Love Thing, Lady Is A Vamp, Say Youll Be There, Naked, Two Become One, Sisters Are Doing It For Themselves, Wannabe, Spice up Your Life, Mama, Viva Forever, Never Give Up On The Goodtimes, and We Are Family. This was the last concert of the Spice Girls world tour which lasted from Febuary to September, performed over 100, and played to over 3 million fans. The only flaw of this concert was ofcourse Geri's absence but now she is doing her own thing so this show the there really is GIRL POWER!!!
